If vſury be an vnlawfull trade,Dr. Smith in Willet on Leuiticus p. 632. as hath beene ſufficiently proued before; then it will follow, that what is wrongfully gotten muſt be reſtored home, and reſtitution be made of the wrong done.Vſurers to reſtore. So Zacheus profeſſeth to recompence foure fold what he deceitfully had gotten; the word is [
