                  ] taken from ſuch as among the Athenians diſcouered thoſe which carryed out figs, which was forbidden, (they being had their in great price,) and ſo the word is generally applied to thoſe, that accuſe others wrongfully, and forge any cauillation againſt them, in like manner Vſurers haue trickes, and deuices to enwrap and entangle their poore debters.Vſurers haue trickes to entangle their debters.
